<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Brown Bros cuts Novell.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Brown Bros cuts Novell.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Brown Brothers Harriman said analyst Richard Scocozza downgraded Novell Inc to a short-term avoid from hold.</p>
<p>-- He cut the stock's long-term rating to underperform from market perform.</p>
<p>-- Cut 1997 earnings per share estimate to $0.65 from $0.90 and introduced a 1998 estimate at $0.65.</p>
<p>-- Said the company's first quarter results were &quot;worse than expected.&quot;</p>
<p>-- The stock was off 2-1/8 to 10-3/4.</p>
</text>
